<br>
In the arena zone you can cast on your pet and dispell him.  Anywhere else, you can not.<br>
<br>
Of course the necro will be wanting to get rid of your pet immediately.  Keep spelleffects on and watch for the spell type.  If it looks like hes casting root or fear type spells, immediately start casting annul on your pet.<br>
<br>
Dont forget banishment will outright kill his pet.  Once you can fully control your pet and he has no pet, hes toast. <p><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg" align="center"><br>
