<br>
Necro fears/roots/darkness/st mage pet. Dispel mage pet and fears/roots/darkness/st gone. Leave first buff slot on pet open to make this easy or don't buff pet.<br>
<br>
Necro dots mage. Mage dispells or cures dot(cure disease and poisen potions)<br>
<br>
Necro roots/darkness/ST mage. Mage will resists due to MR. Pet can be dispelled to remove root/darkenss/ST<br>
<br>
Necro has sow/run3 to outrun your pet-&gt;sow pet(potion) and dispell necro.<br>
<br>
The weeknesses are the following. Mage needs to either nuke necro or kill him with pet. Necro can resist mage nukes with MR+FR equipment. Mala might not be enough to make him hitable. The necro may be able to out run magepet with run3.<br>
<br>
